snippet.title: Shin'en: Nano Assault Neo (Wii U) Full Trailer
snippet.description:
Stop the deadly Nanostray virus from spreading in the nano cosmos. 
Traverse a breathtaking microscopic world. 
You are one against millions.
Coming soon to Nintendo eShop on Wii U!

Download a high-quality version of this trailer at
http://www.nanoassaultgame.com
